# 1password reference file. Safe to commit. `op run --env-file .env.template`
# resolves these at invocation time and exports to the child process only.
#
# Path convention: op://<vault>/<item>/<field>. Adjust if your vault names
# differ; everything here should live in DeLoSecrets.

